title: Mahjongg Investigations Under Suspicion
description:
Organized crime is taking over Metro City! As a detective in the 83rd precinct, use your Mahjongg
skills to unearth clues and bring the criminals to justice! Investigate a vast cityscape with more
than 20 locations where you&#039;ll collect and match evidence tiles to pinpoint perpetrators. Special
clue tiles reveal hidden information and mini-games throughout allow you to interrogate, analyze,
and close the case! Build your career as you make the streets safe for the good people of Metro City!
